@NODE WhatIs "What/Why is aMI-hELP? - © 1996 tRESPASS/mYSTiC"
                         .---------------------------.
                         |      What is aMI-hELP     |
                         `---------------------------'

   aMI-hELP is only the second Ami-Express help door I have seen. This door
   is not just the same as the other one by ?? of ?? I cannot even remember
   This Help door is Brilliant! (even if I do say so myself :-))

   The ansi output is excellent with a Guest mYSTiC ansi from @{"pAINT/cLIQUE" link Contact}
   a brilliant up-and-coming ascii artist.

   Now I guess You may be wondering why I wrote such a door as aMI-hELP.!!
   Buggered if I know!  No. There really was a reason. To use Express
   naturally It requires a high level of inteligance. Some people namely
   the leechers on your board simply dont have this inteligance level 
   required. So I wrote this for them leechers.

   Also it is for people who are new to express so they can pick it up
   quicker than of normal useage.

   aMI-hELP is coded in 1oo% ASM POWER for fastest reactions to Your push
   of a button :))

   I wrote this door in a couple of days. the most time consumming part 
   was to add in all the help texts arrgh! was that boreing!, but I am
   happy with the final results of this fine mYSTiC door and I hope You
   enjoy its use??
  
   (Not that Youll need it) :))
                                                      
                                                       -tRESPASS/mYSTiC
@ENDNODE

